<section id="about" class="py-20 px-6 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">About</h2>
    <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-teal-500 rounded mb-8"></div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          I'm a PMP-certified biomedical engineer with hands-on experience coordinating projects in both startup and academic environments. Working at the intersection of biology and engineering, I naturally took on responsibilities beyond pure R&amp;D — coordinating cross-functional teams, aligning priorities, tracking timelines, and improving workflows.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          I thrive in roles where I can work closely with motivated, collaborative teams, support onboarding and communication, and build systems that make work clearer and more organized.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          I'm particularly interested in opportunities in healthtech, startups, and mission-driven companies where I can combine my technical background with strong organizational and people-focused skills.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-5">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Certification</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-700 font-medium">PMP&reg; — Project Management Professional</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Location</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-700 font-medium">Berlin, Germany</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Languages</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 rounded-full text-sm">English</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 rounded-full text-sm">German (B2)</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 rounded-full text-sm">Farsi (native)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Interests</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-teal-50 text-teal-700 rounded-full text-sm">Healthtech</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-teal-50 text-teal-700 rounded-full text-sm">Startups</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-teal-50 text-teal-700 rounded-full text-sm">Innovation</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
